<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_script_fix">
    <sys_script_fix action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE">
        <before>false</before>
        <description>Add missing Model Category OOB data with empty Asset Class, only if a Model Category for CI Class doesn't already exist</description>
        <name>Fix records in Model Category</name>
        <record_for_rollback>false</record_for_rollback>
        <script><![CDATA[fixRecordsInModelCategory();

function fixRecordsInModelCategory() {
	var gr = new GlideRecord('cmdb_model_category');
	var modelCategoryObj = getModelCategoryObj();
	for (var sysId in modelCategoryObj) {
		gr.initialize();
		gr.get(sysId);
		
		var cmdbCiClass = modelCategoryObj[sysId]['cmdb_ci_class'];
		
		if (!gr.isValidRecord() && !gs.nil(cmdbCiClass) && !doesRecordExist(cmdbCiClass)) {
			insertModelCategoryRecord(sysId, modelCategoryObj[sysId]);
		}
	}
}

function doesRecordExist(cmdbCiClass) {
	var gr = new GlideRecord('cmdb_model_category');
	gr.addQuery('cmdb_ci_class', cmdbCiClass);
	gr.setLimit(1);
	gr.query();
	return gr.hasNext();
}

function insertModelCategoryRecord(sysId, modelCategoryRecordObj) {
	var gr = new GlideRecord('cmdb_model_category');
	gr.initialize();
	gr.setNewGuidValue(sysId);
	for (var key in modelCategoryRecordObj) {
		if (key === 'matched') {//'matched' is not column so skip it
			continue;
		}
		var val = modelCategoryRecordObj[key];
		if (val === 'null' || key === 'asset_class') {
			gr.setValue(key, 'NULL');
		} else {
			gr.setValue(key, val);
		}
	}
	gr.insert();
}
